+for protocol version 1 and
+.Dq rsa
+or
+.Dq dsa
+for protocol version 2.
+.It Fl U Ar reader
+Upload an existing RSA private key into the smartcard in
+.Ar reader .
+.It Fl V Ar validity_interval
+Specify a validity interval when signing a certificate.
